---
title: English-Style Lamb Stew with Mushrooms
description: Grab a woolly sweater and throw a log on the fire. We're upgrading this English countryside stew with tender lamb, earthy mushroom and sweet celery!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/english-style-lamb-stew-15011c4a.jpg
